{
  "stem": "13471.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we went down to see the PX officer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I explained my point of view, and Sieg explained his point of view.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the PX officer-- I have complete orders not to give any foreign nationals any PX materials.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we walked out of there, and I said, Sieg, we didn't get anywhere on that deal.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I said, what are you going to do?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Well, I got to thinking about something else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "About two days later, I said, Sieg, whatever happened about those girls in the printing press?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He says, sir, we're printing books.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I said, huh?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I didn't ask him how he arranged it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I didn't ask him what he had done.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But I'm sure there was some PX material.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "How much time did it take to assemble the record?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Quite a while.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By the time I left-- there were-- there were 24 volumes of proceedings-- verbatim proceedings, from the trial-- the [INAUDIBLE] trial.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then there were 20-- 20 volumes or 21 volumes--  I'm not sure-- of backup documents, supporting documents, which makes a total of 40-odd-- what was it? 42 or 43-- volumes altogether.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, we had to do 2,500 copies of this into German, 2,500 copies into French, 2,500 copies into Russian, 5,000 into English-- 2,500 for the British, 2,500 for the US.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You multiply that all out, friend, and you are talking about half a million volumes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a huge job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it wasn't completed until about six months after the end of the trial.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sieg sent me copies.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say May of '47.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Philadelphia.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Lansdowne.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the fall of-- of a-- of a, '45. '46.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, go back to my academic career.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- they had asked me, didn't I want to stay in the navy?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
